articles.author: Simone McCarthy
articles.title: Leaked Pentagon documents provide snapshot of US intelligence officials watching China - CNN
articles.description: A set of highly classified Pentagon documents that leaked online in recent weeks in an apparent major security breach reveal American intelligence gathering on its key partners, adversaries and competitors -- including China.
